      "raw_text": "The open shop will be the topic\nof debate in the oratorical contest\nhere next Friday afternoon be-\ntween the high schools of Palouse\nCity and Spokane. The debate will\nbe held in the high school audi\nforum and great interest is being\nmanifested in the meeting. A\n\n\nAS it will be debated the ques-\nton reads: Resolved, That the\nlabor unions are justified in insist\ning, through all lawful means at\ntheir disposal, on the closed shop\"\nSpokane will take the affirmative,\nwith Miss Fac Dyke, Willard Nc\nInturff and Arnold Eggerth as its\nchampions. Palouse has three of\nits best takers in training for the\ndefense of the negative PROPOSE\nton."
    }
